title: Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring
description: Gift the one you love the Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring. Hand-finished in sterling silver, this piece is inspired by classic Pandora design elements. Present this style to someone special to show how much you care.

title: Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring Set
description: Classic stackable ring set that is both sleek and elegant. The sparkling heart design styled with the polished wishbone is an absolutely stunning pair that can be worn with any outfit.

title: Celestial Sparkling Sun Ring
description: Radiate summer energy with the Celestial Sparkling Sun Ring. This hand-finished ring glows in 14k gold-plating, with a sun motif in the centre formed by a circle of clear pavé with rays emanating from one side. Wear it by itself as a symbol of energy, positivity and life, or stack it with its counterpart, the Celestial Blue Sparkling Moon Ring. The two rings fit perfectly together, representing duality and harmony in nature and within ourselves.

title: Double Heart Sparkling Ring
description: The Double Heart Sparkling Ring features two heart-shaped clear cubic zirconia nestled together at different angles to symbolize the love between a mother and child. The ring shank is accented with a half row of pavé and is asymmetrically attached to the two hearts for a more modern look. A gift that celebrates everything Mom’s done for you.

title: Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Ring
description: Our Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Ring features three central stones in a petal shape, two marquise-shaped and one pear-shaped. Crafted from sterling silver, this elegant ring is inspired by the beauty of nature, with petal silhouettes that will never go out of style. When styled back-to-back, they form a whole cluster motif, giving an air of completeness to your stack.

title: Knotted Hearts Ring
description: Knotted hearts are a symbol of an unbreakable bond and you can display yours with this band ring in sterling silver. The ring is shaped with interlinked hearts that give it a textured feel, perfect for adding dimension to any curated ring stack. Ideal for wearing or gifting, the timeless ring puts a personal spin on ring stacks and looks equally good worn alone.

title: Lots of Love and Sparkle Stacking Ring Set
description: Rose, on rose, on rose and a whole lotta sparkle! This rose gold-plated ring set is absolutely fabulous. Wear it as a ring stack all on one finger or wear one on each finger. Either way, this ring set is sure to slay!

title: Double Heart Sparkling Ring
description: Shining in 14k gold plating, our hand-finished Double Heart Sparkling Ring features two heart-shaped clear cubic zirconia nestled together at different angles to symbolize the feeling of love and closeness between a mother and child. The band is accented with half a row of pavé and is asymmetrically attached to the two hearts for a more modern look. A gift that celebrates everything Mom's done for you.

title: Infinity Knot Ring
description: It's double the love with Pandora’s unique interpretation of the infinity symbol. The iconic knot wraps around the asymmetrically-set center to signify the strength of the connection. This thin sterling silver infinity ring is the perfect representation of an unbreakable bond and a stylish addition to your ring collection. When infinity isn’t enough, try styling this ring with other infinity-inspired pieces to amplify the message and create a statement look.

title: Disney Aladdin Princess Jasmine Ring
description: Stack your favorite stories with Disney x Pandora. Celebrate the 30th anniversary of Disney's classic, Aladdin, with pieces inspired by the brave and self-assured Princess Jasmine. Crafted from sterling silver, this stackable ring features an oval moonlight blue man-made crystal at its center, surrounded with icy blue man-made crystals, referencing Princess Jasmine's characteristic teal blue color. Make your own wishes come true and layer this sterling silver ring into your everyday favorites to let your bravery shine for all to see - or gift it to an Aladdin fan and take their jewelry into a new world.

title: Disney Beauty and the Beast Rose Ring
description: Be transported into a magical world with the Disney Beauty and the Beast Rose Ring. Inspired by the enchanted rose from the movie, the ring features a red cubic zirconia stone rose in the center of the band, surrounded by openwork leaves and curved branches along with three smaller red stones. Celebrating the imperfect but magical love between Disney's Belle and the Beast, the ring makes an elegant, whimsical addition to any look.

title: Sparkling Red Heart Ring
description: Our jewelry is defined by the things you love. Bring meaning to this dainty solitaire style by wearing it as part of your signature look or sharing with someone special. It's made from sterling silver that's set with a heart-shaped red cubic zirconia flanked by smaller stones. The shank is inscribed with the message "You & me".

title: Disney Tinker Bell Sparkling Ring
description: Find magic in every moment with our Disney Tinker Bell Sparkling Ring. Hand-finished in sterling silver and sparkling cubic zirconia, Tinker Bell is primed for adventure atop a scene of stars and pixie dust. "I can fly" is engraved in the inside of the band as an empowering reminder to always believe in your dreams.

title: Mom Pave Heart Ring
description: A gift for Mum that says it all. The sterling silver Mum Pavé Heart Ring features a ring shank that flows into "Mum" script with three bead-set brilliant-cut clear cubic zirconia decorating the heart. The engraving on the inside of the ring shank reads "LOVE YOU FOREVER", celebrating the devotion of mothers all over the world.

title: Sparkling Twisted Lines Ring
description: Show that style is forever with this sterling silver ring. Made from sterling silver, one of our three signature metals, the glittering band ring is made from twisted lines of pavé-set cubic zirconia. Reminiscent of an infinity symbol, it can be worn for just about any occasion – and also to symbolize a bond of love. Try stacking multiples together for a special occasion.

title: Wrap-Around Arrow Ring
description: Our sterling silver arrow ring is a sleek way to add a symbol of love to your look. The hand-finished ring wraps around your finger to create a stacked effect and is engraved on the inside with the message "Loved". Style it as part of a meaningful ring stack or wear it alone on your index finger as a statement piece. You can also gift it to someone to let them know how you feel about them.

title: Clear Sparkling Crown Ring
description: This dazzling ring is the ultimate crowning glory. Crafted in sterling silver, it is embellished with sparkling cubic zirconia stones and topped with solid bead detailing. Wear it solo or together with other Pandora crown rings to create a look that's fit for every princess.

title: Pink Daisy Flower Trio Ring
description: Bring flower power to your style with this flower crown-inspired Pink Daisy Flower Trio Ring. The daisy ring features a 14k rose gold-plated and is decorated with three enamel flowers with cubic zirconia in the centre. A hand-painted finish brings the vibrant petals to life with delicate shading. Inspired by the daisy, a flower which blooms in adversity and represents freedom, the ring serves as a stylish reminder to stay true to who you are.

title: Pandora Timeless Wish Sparkling Alternating Ring
description: Make eye-catching statements with your everyday jewelry, with our Pandora Timeless Wish Sparkling Alternating Ring, a modern interpretation of classic ring styles. Crafted from polished sterling silver, the ring band is set to sparkle with a row of cubic zirconia in round, marquise and pear-shaped cuts. Wear yours as a single piece or layer with more sparkling Pandora Timeless rings for a modern approach to stacking that will bring timeless elegance to every look.

title: Sparkling Daisy Flower Crown Ring
description: Wear a delicate and beautiful flower crown year-round with the Sparkling Daisy Flower Crown Ring. Featuring a band of daisies with small stones in their centers, the ring is inspired by the strength of the flower that blooms in adversity and symbolizes freedom. The sterling silver ring can be stacked to double up on the flower power or styled with a matching ring in Pandora Rose™, 14k rose gold-plated unique metal blend, for a contrasting look.

title: Pandora Signature Pave & Beads Pendant & Necklace
description: Our classic Pandora Signature design elements have come full circle. Crafted from sterling silver, the Pandora Signature Pavé & Beads Pendant & Necklace features two textured circles, one of which spins for a touch of dynamic movement. Cut-out hearts adorn the pendant’s reverse while a row of pave sparkles on the bail. Two jump rings allow you to adjust the length, making it your perfect go-to piece for any occasion.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant 0.25 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Feel the love with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant. This 14k gold pendant features a unique setting that creates a heart motif with a 0.75 carat lab-grown diamond sparkling at its centre. On the back of the pendant, a heart-shaped cut-out echoes the shape of the setting and lets the light shine through to maximise sparkle. A universal symbol of love, the heart shape makes this pendant the perfect gift to represent a special connection - or an affirmation of the love you have for yourself.

title: Pandora ME Pavé Snake Medallion Charm
description: Make a symbolic statement with our Pandora ME Pavé Snake Medallion Charm, finished with 14k gold plating. A vintage-inspired revival of a classic emblem, this mystical serpent entwines itself around the medallion charm's circular frame, capturing a visual style inspired by tattoo art. Microbead detailing adds texture, bringing the snake to life as a symbol of protection, transformation, healing and rebirth. This medallion charm can be styled on any Pandora ME openable link across link chain bracelets, necklaces, rings and hoops.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Infinity Pendant 0.25 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Embrace endless possibilities with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Infinity Pendant. This 14k gold pendant features a 0.25 carat lab-grown diamond in a unique setting inspired by the infinity symbol. From the front, the setting creates two crescent shapes framing the lab-grown diamond - turn it around to reveal an openwork infinity loop motif forming the setting behind the stone. Wear it as a talisman to symbolise infinity in its many senses: eternal love, limitless potential, all the possibilities life has to offer...

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Star Pendant 0.75 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Look to the stars with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Star Pendant. Stars have been the stuff of legend for as long as we have told stories, often representing hope, guidance and our wishes and dreams. This 14k gold pendant embodies this celestial inspiration, inviting you to give it your own meaning. Five triangular prongs create a star-shaped setting embracing a 0.75 carat round brilliant excellent cut lab-grown diamond. A star-shaped cut-out on the back lets the light shine through, capturing the sparkle of starlight.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant 0.75 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Feel the love with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant. title: Marvel Captain Marvel Octogram Star Two tone Pendant Necklace
description: Bring the power to your collection with the Captain Marvel Octogram Star Two-tone Pendant Necklace. Inspired by MARVEL's Captain Marvel, this necklace in our 14k gold-plated unique metal blend features an eight-point star with a row of pavé on its sides and symbolizes strength and daring. It is engraved with the message "HIGHER FURTHER FASTER", which serves as a reminder to always push for your dreams. It features a sterling silver eight-pointed star with sparkle by the closure and is adjustable to two lengths. Wear the necklace as a symbol, which represents that you hold the qualities you need to succeed or gift it to a superhero you hold dear.

title: Sparkling Double Halo Collier Necklace
description: Elevate your every day look with the Sparkling Double Halo Collier Necklace. Hand-finished in sterling silver, this design includes a pendant featuring one big, raised central stone surrounded by two sparkling halos. The outer halo sits slightly lower than the inner halo, with space in between them to add depth to the design. This necklace includes a lobster clasp, which means its adjustable to two lengths. Style with other shimmering Pandora Timeless designs for an eye-catching combination with a classic finish.

title: Sparkling Family Tree Necklace
description: Show the story of your roots with our family tree necklace pendant, featuring a medallion decorated with a stone-embellished tree - a symbol of those closet to you. The collier style necklace is fitted with a slider clasp that lets you adjust the necklace for the perfect drop. Wear it alone as a statement of your story, layered with other meaningful pieces or gift it to someone that shares your roots.

title: Pandora Moments U-shape Charm Pendant Necklace
description: Give luck a chance with the Pandora Moments U-Shape Charm Pendant Necklace. Reminiscent of the traditional symbol of good fortune - the horseshoe, this pendant in our iconic snake chain pattern can be styled with 2-3 of your favorite Pandora charms. This necklace features two ball clasps connected to the pendant at the top, one of which is openable and it is also adjustable to two lengths. Bring positive energy to your look with this easy-to-personalise charm holder or gift it to the charm collector in your life.

title: Pandora Moments Snake Chain Necklace
description: This sleek snake chain necklace is a sophisticated staple for your Pandora collection. Available in a choice of lengths, it is crafted in sterling silver and finished with an embossed ball clasp. Wear your Pandora necklace unadorned for simple elegance or create a unique look with your personal edit of charms. Complete your styling with some sparkling silicone-lined Pandora clips, a glamorous way arrange and secure your charms.

title: Family Always Encircled Pendant Necklace
description: A symbol of everlasting ties, the Family Always Encircled Pendant Necklace features three entwined circles in the pendant – two polished sterling silver and one sparkling cubic zirconia pavé. The closure features a small heart-shaped disc with the Pandora Crown O monogram on one side. The chain length is adjustable, making this a versatile finishing touch to your outfit.

title: Sparkling Infinity Collier Necklace
description: The delicate infinity collier necklace symbolizes love that lasts for all eternity. It dazzles in sterling silver and features clear cubic zirconia for added sparkle. Inspired by the eternal bond between a mother and a child, the infinity symbol lends gravitas to your emotions and helps you express exactly how you feel with a universally recognized sign for a deep connection. Style with other infinity-inspired pieces or gift the eternity necklace to someone you love to infinity and beyond.

description: Soar to new heights of individual expression with a sterling silver necklace full of celestial style with cubic zirconia details. Featuring a sparkling heart pendant framed by angel wings, the sterling silver necklace evokes the symbol of a guardian angel, who protects and guides you gracefully through life. Wear as a reminder to always bring positive energy to everything that you do or gift as a meaningful present symbolizing love and protection to someone special in your life.

description: Celebrate the special bond you share with your mom with our Mom Pavé Collier Necklace. Crafted in sterling silver, this meaningful piece features the word "Mom" written in script, with the middle letter shaped like a heart and set with three small stones. Fixed in the middle of the collier necklace, this piece is a celebration of all the mother figures that have shaped our lives. The necklace has a sliding clasp for fully adjustable length. Gift this special piece as a reminder of how much Mom means to you and she'll feel the love all year round.

title: Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Pendant Necklace
description: Bring the beauty of nature to your jewelry with the Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Pendant Necklace. This sterling silver necklace features a cluster of alternating pear and marquise-shaped stones around a round center stone, forming a geometric shape inspired by petal and leaf elements. An elegant reinterpretation of the shapes we find in nature, this necklace is perfect for bringing a delicate, floating feel to your looks.

title: Pandora Moments Studded Chain Necklace
description: Update your jewelry collection with our Pandora Moments Studded Chain Necklace in our 14k gold-plated unique metal blend. This necklace can be styled with any size of the Pandora Moments O Pendant or Heart Charm Pendant. Please note that the clasp cannot be styled with any charms.

description: Discover the diamond necklace as unique as you. Our Pandora Infinite Sterling Silver Lab-grown Diamond Drop Necklace features two round brilliant excellent cut lab-grown diamonds, totaling 0.30 carat. One is placed in the centre of the chain, while the other dangles from the drop chain, creating a dramatic Y-shaped design. A prong-and-partial-bezel setting creates a floating effect for each diamond. Inspired by infinite connections, the modern infinity shape flows seamlessly around the stones and represents your eternal bonds. Each Pandora Lab-grown diamond is treated with a post-growth colour enhancement called annealing.

title: Pandora ME Double Link Chain Necklace
description: Your self-expression journey starts here: this 14k gold-plated Pandora ME Double Link Chain Necklace has endless styling possibilities to choose from, featuring two openable links - designed with grooved lines to set them apart - five links between each openable link and a small carabiner clasp closure. Half of the necklace links up to a double chain detail, adding an individual edge to the chain. You can keep the original length, make your link chain longer or turn it into a choker, all by adding and taking away links to suit you. Once you’ve customised your link chain, remix it with meaningful medallion charms and mini dangle charms on the openable links to tell your story.

title: Two-Tone Floating Curved Feather Collier Necklace
description: Catch the season's light with our Two-tone Floating Curved Feather Collier Necklace. This necklace features a 14k rose gold-plated feather detailed with sparkling cubic zirconia on one half and polished metal on the other. The tip of the feather curves around the jump ring that fixes it to the sterling silver chain, giving the illusion it is floating across your neck. The end of the chain is hand-finished with a round disc engraved with the Pandora Crown O and three jump rings for versatile styling. Wear this whimsical collier necklace with other 14k rose gold-plated pieces to enhance your spring glow.

description: This radiant lab-grown diamond necklace features modern interpretations of infinity motifs, set on a long 14k white gold box chain that can be doubled up for layered styling. title: Disney The Little Mermaid Seashell Stud Earrings
description: Come out of your shell with our Disney The Little Mermaid Seashell Stud Earrings. Each 14k gold-plated earring is detailed with realistic grooved lines and set with a luminous white lacquered artificial pearl. Add them to your collection as a reminder that there is an ocean of possibilities waiting for you.

title: Marvel The Avengers Infinity Stones Hoop Earrings
description: Power up your look with our Marvel Infinity Stones Hoop Earrings. Representing the most coveted objects in the universe, these 14k gold-plated earrings feature six colourful man-made crystals set in alternating marquise, circle and square shapes. The side of each shape is engraved with its stone's corresponding symbolic power: "SPACE", "POWER", "TIME", "REALITY", "SOUL" and "MIND". Style them the same direction for a perfectly balanced look, or switch them to show every colour of the rainbow.

title: Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Drop Earrings
description: Bring the beauty of nature to your jewelry with our Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Drop Earrings. These statement designs feature gracefully tumbling stones that fall from a central cluster of round, pear-shaped and marquise-shaped cubic zirconia, forming a geometric shape inspired by petal and leaf elements. An elegant reinterpretation of the shapes we find in nature, these 14k rose gold-plated sparkling drop earrings are perfect for bringing a touch of the natural world to your everyday looks.

title: Pandora Infinite Lab-grown Diamond Drop Earrings 0.30 ct tw Sterling Silver
description: Our Pandora Infinite Sterling Silver Lab-grown Diamond Drop Earrings were designed to shine like every facet of you. Hand-set in sterling silver, each earring features two infinity loops linked together to create an elegant drop style. A celebration of beauty in simplicity, the top loop is open. A round brilliant excellent cut lab-grown diamond is suspended in the bottom loop, appearing to float in its prong-and-partial-bezel setting. The modern design flows seamlessly around each stone, totaling 0.30 carat, to represent your eternal bonds. Each Pandora Lab-grown diamond is treated with a post-growth colour enhancement called annealing.

title: Sparkling Swallow Stud Earrings
description: Say hello to spring with our Sparkling Swallow Stud Earrings. Symbolizing hope for better days to come, these sterling silver earrings feature a swallow detailed with microbeads, grooved feather lines and pavé in varying shades of blue. Each carries a round brilliant-cut deep blue man-made crystal in its beak, appearing to give it a sweet peck. Style these studs with other swallow-inspired jewelry for a look that channels the spirit of the season.

title: Pandora Infinite Lab-grown Diamond Stud Earrings 0.50 ct tw 14k White Gold
description: A pair of solid 14k white gold stud earrings each hand set with a 0.25 carat lab-grown diamond. A sparkling celebration of the infinite potential within all of us, these earrings feature a radiant round brilliant excellent cut lab-grown diamond suspended in our modern infinity setting. Each Pandora Lab-grown diamond is treated with a post-growth colour enhancement called annealing.

title: Deep Purple Pansy Flower Stud Earrings
description: Add depth and color to your spring looks with our Deep Purple Pansy Flower Stud Earrings. Set in 14k rose gold plating, each pansy features two petals covered in sparkling pavé and three petals hand-painted in rich enamel, making every flower completely unique. The newest flower to grace our garden, pansies symbolize love in its many forms. Wear them as a reminder of all the loved ones in your life. Create a bold spring look by pairing these with our matching Deep Purple Pansy Flower Ring.

title: Rectangular Sparkling Halo Stud Earrings
description: Wear the halo effect. Our Rectangular Sparkling Halo Stud Earrings bring classic elegance to your everyday look, crafted from sterling silver with rectangular radiant-cut cubic zirconia stones. Finished with a halo of pavé that reaches around one half of each earring, these sparkling statements reinterpret traditional halo aesthetics to create modern jewelry box staples.

title: Pandora Moments Heart Charm Hoop Earrings
description: Earrings you’ll fall in love with. Crafted in sterling silver with Pandora’s iconic snake chain pattern, these asymmetric hoops are a reminder that true love is never uniform. Wear these symbols of self-love on their own, or style up to three of your charms, dangles and pendants and tell the world your story.

title: Floating Curved Feather Stud Earrings
description: Catch the season's light with our Floating Curved Feather Stud Earrings. These 14k rose gold-plated studs feature a feather detailed with sparkling cubic zirconia on one half and polished metal on the other. Each is curved to delicately hug your ear. Style these whimsical earrings with other 14k rose gold-plated pieces to enhance your spring glow.

title: Pandora Signature Two-tone Logo Circles Stud Earrings
description: Our iconic pendant reimagined as studs. The Pandora Signature Two-tone Logo Circles Stud Earrings feature a 14k rose-gold plated circle with sparkling pavé, inside a polished sterling silver circle featuring the Pandora logo. A butterfly back ensures a secure and comfortable fit. This dynamic piece combines much-loved motifs of the collection, making it perfect for pairing with other Pandora Signature jewelry.

title: Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Stud Earrings
description: Bring the beauty of nature to your jewelry with our Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Stud Earrings. These sterling silver studs feature a pair of marquise-cut and pear-shaped stones around a round center stone, forming a geometric shape inspired by petal and leaf elements. An elegant reinterpretation of the shapes we find in nature, these sparkling studs are perfect for bringing a delicate feel to your everyday looks.

title: Open Heart Stud Earrings
description: A heart doesn't have to be big to be filled with love. Our dainty earring studs are cast from sterling silver, one of our three signature metals. The open heart design is carefully set by hand with cubic zirconia for subtle sparkle as they catch the light. Wear them traditionally, as a pair, or individually as part of a curated earring stack.

title: Sparkling Asymmetric Stars Stud Earrings
description: Bring celestial sparkle to your look with these Sparkling Asymmetric Stars Stud Earrings. Hand-finished in sterling silver with sparkling cubic zirconia stones, the earrings feature asymmetric stars covered with pavé and micro beads. These versatile studs, inspired by the beauty of the night sky, will add a touch of sparkle to every look. Let them shine bright on their own or mix and match them with other Pandora stud earrings for an eclectic, modern look.

title: Double Band Pavé Hoop Earrings
description: Elevate any ensemble with the Double Band Pavé Hoop Earrings. Hand-finished in sterling silver, the hoops feature two bands, one of which features a row of smaller sparkling clear cubic zirconia pavé, the other of which features a row of larger pavé. Differently sized stones and settings lend a contemporary twist to a classic hoop earring, bringing these classics into a new era. Wear them alone or with a sparkling necklace to make any look shine.

title: Square Sparkle Hoop Earrings
description: Do you find yourself drawn to both classic and contemporary styles at once? Wear a set of sparkling hoop earrings that bring together the best of both worlds in a playful and daring way. Our sterling silver hoop earrings with square cubic zirconia detail from our updated Timeless Elegance collection encompass glowing, clear stones dotted around a classic hoop earring for a completely modern and elevated style you can wear every day.

title: Sparkling Wave Stud Earrings
description: Elegant and unexpected, our Sparkling Wave Stud Earrings are a contemporary way to add a little sparkle to your everyday look. Hand-finished in sterling silver, these studs are set with an eye-catching brilliant-cut clear cubic zirconia in the dip of a pavé wave. Pair them with other wave styles from Pandora Timeless for an artistic take on sparkle.

title: Disney Mickey Mouse & Minnie Mouse Silhouette Stud Earrings
description: Celebrate true romance with the Disney Mickey Mouse & Minnie Mouse Silhouette Stud Earrings. Hand-finished in sterling silver, this mismatched set of studs is inspired by the famous sweethearts with one depicting Mickey Mouse’s profile and the other Minnie Mouse. Each earring features a clear heart-shaped stone at its center. Style these with a heart-shaped sterling silver pendant for a look with filled love.

title: Sparkling Circle Stud Earrings
description: Jewelry trends come and go, but the circle remains an enduring symbol of style – and an emblem of forever. This pair of stud earrings is cast in sterling silver and set with cubic zirconia for a subtly sparkling finish. Wear individually to add a graphic touch to earring stacks or style as a pair for a cool take on everyday earrings. Who said geometry was boring

title: Sparkling Freehand Heart Hoop Earrings
description: Add a little love to your earring styling with our Sparkling Freehand Heart Hoop Earrings. Each earring holds a freehand heart set with clear cubic zirconia, a symbol of perfectly imperfect love. Featuring sterling silver hoops and 14k rose gold-plated hearts, these special earrings are eye-catching and heart-melting in equal measure.

title: Family Always Encircled Hoop Earrings
description: A symbol of unbreakable bonds, the Family Always Encircled Hoop Earrings each feature three circles entwined on a hoop – two polished sterling silver and one decorated with a row of clear cubic zirconia pavé. The harmony of various shapes symbolizes how families come together despite their differences.

title: Double Heart Sparkling Stud Earrings
description: Love at first sparkle. The Double Heart Sparkling Stud Earrings each feature two heart-shaped cubic zirconia stones. A modern take on a classic design, it’s the perfect gift for someone special or a well-deserved treat for yourself.

title: Sparkling Double Halo Stud Earrings
description: Let your ears do the talking with these Sparkling Double Halo Stud Earrings. Hand-finished in sterling silver, each stud features one big, raised central stone surrounded by two halos decorated with clear cubic zirconia. The outer halo sits slightly lower than the inner halo, with space in between them to add depth to the design. The outer halo is a detatchable earring jacket, so the earring can be styled with or without it. Style with a shimmering sterling silver bracelet for a sophisticated look.

title: Pandora Signature Pave & Beads Pendant & Necklace
description: Our classic Pandora Signature design elements have come full circle. Crafted from sterling silver, the Pandora Signature Pavé & Beads Pendant & Necklace features two textured circles, one of which spins for a touch of dynamic movement. Cut-out hearts adorn the pendant’s reverse while a row of pave sparkles on the bail. Two jump rings allow you to adjust the length, making it your perfect go-to piece for any occasion.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant 0.25 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Feel the love with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant. This 14k gold pendant features a unique setting that creates a heart motif with a 0.75 carat lab-grown diamond sparkling at its centre. On the back of the pendant, a heart-shaped cut-out echoes the shape of the setting and lets the light shine through to maximise sparkle. A universal symbol of love, the heart shape makes this pendant the perfect gift to represent a special connection - or an affirmation of the love you have for yourself.

title: Pandora ME Pavé Snake Medallion Charm
description: Make a symbolic statement with our Pandora ME Pavé Snake Medallion Charm, finished with 14k gold plating. A vintage-inspired revival of a classic emblem, this mystical serpent entwines itself around the medallion charm's circular frame, capturing a visual style inspired by tattoo art. Microbead detailing adds texture, bringing the snake to life as a symbol of protection, transformation, healing and rebirth. This medallion charm can be styled on any Pandora ME openable link across link chain bracelets, necklaces, rings and hoops.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Infinity Pendant 0.25 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Embrace endless possibilities with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Infinity Pendant. This 14k gold pendant features a 0.25 carat lab-grown diamond in a unique setting inspired by the infinity symbol. From the front, the setting creates two crescent shapes framing the lab-grown diamond - turn it around to reveal an openwork infinity loop motif forming the setting behind the stone. Wear it as a talisman to symbolise infinity in its many senses: eternal love, limitless potential, all the possibilities life has to offer...

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Star Pendant 0.75 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Look to the stars with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Star Pendant. Stars have been the stuff of legend for as long as we have told stories, often representing hope, guidance and our wishes and dreams. This 14k gold pendant embodies this celestial inspiration, inviting you to give it your own meaning. Five triangular prongs create a star-shaped setting embracing a 0.75 carat round brilliant excellent cut lab-grown diamond. A star-shaped cut-out on the back lets the light shine through, capturing the sparkle of starlight.

title: Pandora Talisman Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant 0.75 carat tw 14k Gold
description: Feel the love with the Pandora Talisman 14k Gold Lab-grown Diamond Heart Pendant. title: Marvel Captain Marvel Octogram Star Two tone Pendant Necklace
description: Bring the power to your collection with the Captain Marvel Octogram Star Two-tone Pendant Necklace. Inspired by MARVEL's Captain Marvel, this necklace in our 14k gold-plated unique metal blend features an eight-point star with a row of pavé on its sides and symbolizes strength and daring. It is engraved with the message "HIGHER FURTHER FASTER", which serves as a reminder to always push for your dreams. It features a sterling silver eight-pointed star with sparkle by the closure and is adjustable to two lengths. Wear the necklace as a symbol, which represents that you hold the qualities you need to succeed or gift it to a superhero you hold dear.

title: Sparkling Double Halo Collier Necklace
description: Elevate your every day look with the Sparkling Double Halo Collier Necklace. Hand-finished in sterling silver, this design includes a pendant featuring one big, raised central stone surrounded by two sparkling halos. The outer halo sits slightly lower than the inner halo, with space in between them to add depth to the design. This necklace includes a lobster clasp, which means its adjustable to two lengths. Style with other shimmering Pandora Timeless designs for an eye-catching combination with a classic finish.

title: Sparkling Family Tree Necklace
description: Show the story of your roots with our family tree necklace pendant, featuring a medallion decorated with a stone-embellished tree - a symbol of those closet to you. The collier style necklace is fitted with a slider clasp that lets you adjust the necklace for the perfect drop. Wear it alone as a statement of your story, layered with other meaningful pieces or gift it to someone that shares your roots.

title: Pandora Moments U-shape Charm Pendant Necklace
description: Give luck a chance with the Pandora Moments U-Shape Charm Pendant Necklace. Reminiscent of the traditional symbol of good fortune - the horseshoe, this pendant in our iconic snake chain pattern can be styled with 2-3 of your favorite Pandora charms. This necklace features two ball clasps connected to the pendant at the top, one of which is openable and it is also adjustable to two lengths. Bring positive energy to your look with this easy-to-personalise charm holder or gift it to the charm collector in your life.

description: Galanterie de Cartier ring, white gold (750/1000), black lacquer, set with a brilliant-cut diamond available in 1.50 to 1.69 carats and paved with brilliant-cut diamonds.

title: ETINCELLE DE CARTIER RING
description: Étincelle de Cartier ring, rose gold (750/1000), set with a pear-shaped diamond center stone totaling 0.16 carat and 22 brilliant-cut diamonds totaling 0.10 carat. Width: 1.52 mm. Thickness: 1.35 mm.

title: VENDÔME LOUIS CARTIER WEDDING BAND
description: Vendôme Louis Cartier Wedding Band, rose gold (750/1000), 18K white gold (750/1000), 18K yellow gold (750/1000), set with 53 brilliant-cut diamonds totaling 0.23 carats. Width: 3.5 mm (for size 52).

title: HIGH JEWELRY RING
description: Ring - platinum, one 16.20-carat triangular-shaped blue-green tourmaline, black lacquer, brilliant-cut diamonds.

title: Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring
description: Gift the one you love the Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring. Hand-finished in sterling silver, this piece is inspired by classic Pandora design elements. The heart detail has been incorporated into the series' iconic V-shape to create a heartfelt design. Clear cubic zirconia decorate the heart and top of the ring shank. Present this style to someone special to show how much you care.

title: Sparkling Wishbone Heart Ring Set
description: Classic stackable ring set that is both sleek and elegant. The sparkling heart design styled with the polished wishbone is an absolutely stunning pair that can be worn with any outfit.

title: Celestial Sparkling Sun Ring
description: Radiate summer energy with the Celestial Sparkling Sun Ring. This hand-finished ring glows in 14k gold-plating, with a sun motif in the centre formed by a circle of clear pavé with rays emanating from one side. Wear it by itself as a symbol of energy, positivity and life, or stack it with its counterpart, the Celestial Blue Sparkling Moon Ring. The two rings fit perfectly together, representing duality and harmony in nature and within ourselves.

title: Double Heart Sparkling Ring
description: The Double Heart Sparkling Ring features two heart-shaped clear cubic zirconia nestled together at different angles to symbolize the love between a mother and child. The ring shank is accented with a half row of pavé and is asymmetrically attached to the two hearts for a more modern look. A gift that celebrates everything Mom’s done for you.

title: Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Ring
description: Our Sparkling Herbarium Cluster Ring features three central stones in a petal shape, two marquise-shaped and one pear-shaped. Crafted from sterling silver, this elegant ring is inspired by the beauty of nature, with petal silhouettes that will never go out of style. When styled back-to-back, they form a whole cluster motif, giving an air of completeness to your stack.

title: Knotted Hearts Ring
description: Knotted hearts are a symbol of an unbreakable bond and you can display yours with this band ring in sterling silver. The ring is shaped with interlinked hearts that give it a textured feel, perfect for adding dimension to any curated ring stack. Ideal for wearing or gifting, the timeless ring puts a personal spin on ring stacks and looks equally good worn alone.

title: Lots of Love and Sparkle Stacking Ring Set
description: Rose, on rose, on rose and a whole lotta sparkle! This rose gold-plated ring set is absolutely fabulous. Wear it as a ring stack all on one finger or wear one on each finger. Either way, this ring set is sure to slay!

title: Double Heart Sparkling Ring
description: Shining in 14k gold plating, our hand-finished Double Heart Sparkling Ring features two heart-shaped clear cubic zirconia nestled together at different angles to symbolize the feeling of love and closeness between a mother and child. The band is accented with half a row of pavé and is asymmetrically attached to the two hearts for a more modern look. A gift that celebrates everything Mom's done for you.

title: Infinity Knot Ring
description: It's double the love with Pandora’s unique interpretation of the infinity symbol. The iconic knot wraps around the asymmetrically-set center to signify the strength of the connection. This thin sterling silver infinity ring is the perfect representation of an unbreakable bond and a stylish addition to your ring collection. When infinity isn’t enough, try styling this ring with other infinity-inspired pieces to amplify the message and create a statement look.

title: Disney Aladdin Princess Jasmine Ring
description: Stack your favorite stories with Disney x Pandora. Celebrate the 30th anniversary of Disney's classic, Aladdin, with pieces inspired by the brave and self-assured Princess Jasmine. Crafted from sterling silver, this stackable ring features an oval moonlight blue man-made crystal at its center, surrounded with icy blue man-made crystals, referencing Princess Jasmine's characteristic teal blue color. Make your own wishes come true and layer this sterling silver ring into your everyday favorites to let your bravery shine for all to see - or gift it to an Aladdin fan and take their jewelry into a new world.

title: Disney Beauty and the Beast Rose Ring
description: Be transported into a magical world with the Disney Beauty and the Beast Rose Ring. Inspired by the enchanted rose from the movie, the ring features a red cubic zirconia stone rose in the center of the band, surrounded by openwork leaves and curved branches along with three smaller red stones. Celebrating the imperfect but magical love between Disney's Belle and the Beast, the ring makes an elegant, whimsical addition to any look.

title: Sparkling Red Heart Ring
description: Our jewelry is defined by the things you love. Bring meaning to this dainty solitaire style by wearing it as part of your signature look or sharing with someone special. It's made from sterling silver that's set with a heart-shaped red cubic zirconia flanked by smaller stones. The shank is inscribed with the message "You & me".

title: Disney Tinker Bell Sparkling Ring
description: Find magic in every moment with our Disney Tinker Bell Sparkling Ring. Hand-finished in sterling silver and sparkling cubic zirconia, Tinker Bell is primed for adventure atop a scene of stars and pixie dust. "I can fly" is engraved in the inside of the band as an empowering reminder to always believe in your dreams.

title: Mom Pave Heart Ring
description: A gift for Mum that says it all. The sterling silver Mum Pavé Heart Ring features a ring shank that flows into "Mum" script with three bead-set brilliant-cut clear cubic zirconia decorating the heart. The engraving on the inside of the ring shank reads "LOVE YOU FOREVER", celebrating the devotion of mothers all over the world.

title: Sparkling Twisted Lines Ring
description: Show that style is forever with this sterling silver ring. Made from sterling silver, one of our three signature metals, the glittering band ring is made from twisted lines of pavé-set cubic zirconia. Reminiscent of an infinity symbol, it can be worn for just about any occasion – and also to symbolize a bond of love. Try stacking multiples together for a special occasion.

title: Wrap-Around Arrow Ring
description: Our sterling silver arrow ring is a sleek way to add a symbol of love to your look. The hand-finished ring wraps around your finger to create a stacked effect and is engraved on the inside with the message "Loved". Style it as part of a meaningful ring stack or wear it alone on your index finger as a statement piece. You can also gift it to someone to let them know how you feel about them.

title: Clear Sparkling Crown Ring
description: This dazzling ring is the ultimate crowning glory. Crafted in sterling silver, it is embellished with sparkling cubic zirconia stones and topped with solid bead detailing. Wear it solo or together with other Pandora crown rings to create a look that's fit for every princess.

title: Pink Daisy Flower Trio Ring
description: Bring flower power to your style with this flower crown-inspired Pink Daisy Flower Trio Ring. The daisy ring features a 14k rose gold-plated and is decorated with three enamel flowers with cubic zirconia in the centre. A hand-painted finish brings the vibrant petals to life with delicate shading. Inspired by the daisy, a flower which blooms in adversity and represents freedom, the ring serves as a stylish reminder to stay true to who you are.

title: Pandora Timeless Wish Sparkling Alternating Ring
description: Make eye-catching statements with your everyday jewelry, with our Pandora Timeless Wish Sparkling Alternating Ring, a modern interpretation of classic ring styles. Crafted from polished sterling silver, the ring band is set to sparkle with a row of cubic zirconia in round, marquise and pear-shaped cuts. Wear yours as a single piece or layer with more sparkling Pandora Timeless rings for a modern approach to stacking that will bring timeless elegance to every look.

title: Sparkling Daisy Flower Crown Ring
description: Wear a delicate and beautiful flower crown year-round with the Sparkling Daisy Flower Crown Ring. Featuring a band of daisies with small stones in their centers, the ring is inspired by the strength of the flower that blooms in adversity and symbolizes freedom. The sterling silver ring can be stacked to double up on the flower power or styled with a matching ring in Pandora Rose™, 14k rose gold-plated unique metal blend, for a contrasting look.
